</p><p>Our team was approached by our friends at Heard City to help them establish a brand identity that was true to their agency culture and communicated the leading audio post-production capabilities of the cpmpany. Our creative team worked with the client to capture the esence of the agency and bring the bradn to life in digital form through a responsive HTML5 prallax website and brochure.</p>

